        "task2",
        "task3",
        "task4"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，您是希望用三列来代表三种Groupware工具作为容器，然后把具体的任务类型作为卡片放在对应列下面对吧？第一列我理解为KanbanBoard本身？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "column1"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "对，第一列就是Groupware_KanbanBoard，它下面挂两个任务：WikiPage和SprintBacklog。这两个任务其实是可以在看板内部创建或关联的。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "column1",
        "task1",
        "task2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好的，第一列结构已建立：KanbanBoard列包含WikiPage和SprintBacklog两个任务卡片。现在第二列您打算放什么工具？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "column1",
        "task1",
        "task2"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "第二列放ChatRoom，即时通讯工具。它下面挂一个WikiPage任务，表示在聊天过程中可以快捷创建或引用Wiki页面。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "column2",
        "task3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "收到，ChatRoom列关联WikiPage任务。那第三列应该是IssueTracker？我看到SprintBacklog还没用完。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "column2",
        "task3",
        "column3",
        "task4"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "没错，第三列是IssueTracker，问题追踪器。下面放SprintBacklog，表示从问题直接生成冲刺待办事项。这样三列就完整了：KanbanBoard、ChatRoom、IssueTracker。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "column3",
        "task4"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 8,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "三列结构已完成。我检查一下：KanbanBoard下有WikiPage和SprintBacklog；ChatRoom下有WikiPage；IssueTracker下有SprintBacklog。这样WikiPage和SprintBacklog都在两列中重复出现了，是设计意图吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "column1",
        "column2",
        "column3",
        "task1",
        "task2",
        "task3",
        "task4"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 9,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "是的，这是刻意设计的。同一个任务类型可以在不同工具上下文中被创建或引用，体现Groupware的集成特性。WikiPage既可以从看板创建，也可以从聊天中创建。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "task1",
        "task3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 10,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "理解了，体现跨工具的工作流。不过我刚注意到一个细节——您说的是WikiPage和SprintBacklog作为任务类型，但我在列名上写的是Groupware_KanbanBoard、Groupware_ChatRoom、Groupware_IssueTracker，前缀需要统一吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "column1",
        "column2",
        "column3"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 11,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "前缀统一为Groupware_很好，保持命名空间一致。任务卡片也一样：Groupware_WikiPage、Groupware_SprintBacklog。这样整个图都是Groupware域的对象。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "task1",
        "task2",
        "task3",
        "task4"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 12,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "已全部统一前缀。当前结构：Groupware_KanbanBoard列包含Groupware_WikiPage和Groupware_SprintBacklog；Groupware_ChatRoom列包含Groupware_WikiPage；Groupware_IssueTracker列包含Groupware_SprintBacklog。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "column1",
        "column2",
        "column3",
        "task1",
        "task2",
        "task3",
        "task4"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 13,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "稍等，我再确认一下数量。KanbanBoard列是两个任务，ChatRoom列是一个任务，IssueTracker列是一个任务。总共四个任务卡片，分布是2-1-1，对吧？",
