    {
      "turn_id": 14,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "确认，数量正确。KanbanBoard:2，ChatRoom:1，IssueTracker:1。需要调整分布吗？比如让ChatRoom也挂两个任务？",
      "elements_involved": [
